<p>另一个麻烦些，如下，仅供参考，尽符合我个人审美，一些细节没改。</p>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.post-block</span>, <span class="selector-class">.header-inner</span>, <span class="selector-class">.sidebar-inner</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.use-motion</span> <span class="selector-class">.post-block</span>, <span class="selector-class">.use-motion</span> <span class="selector-class">.pagination</span>, <span class="selector-class">.use-motion</span> <span class="selector-class">.comments</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="number">255</span>,<span class="number">255</span>,<span class="number">255</span>,<span class="number">0.7</span>) <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.sidebar</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">tbody</span> <span class="selector-tag">tr</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:nth-of-type(odd)</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">pre</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background</span>: transparent <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.menu-item-active</span> <span class="selector-tag">a</span>, <span class="selector-class">.menu</span> <span class="selector-class">.menu-item</span> <span class="selector-tag">a</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:hover</span>, <span class="selector-class">.menu</span> <span class="selector-class">.menu-item</span> <span class="selector-tag">span</span><span class="selector-class">.exturl</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:hover</span>, </span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.btn</span>, </span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.highlight</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.hbe-input-container</span> <span class="selector-tag">input</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0.1</span>) <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.highlight</span> <span class="selector-class">.gutter</span> <span class="selector-tag">pre</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#222</span> <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.highlight</span> <span class="selector-class">.gutter</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0.2</span>) <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="图片位置"><a href="#图片位置" class="headerlink" title="图片位置"></a>图片位置</h4><p>使用了<strong>hexo-assert-images</strong>插件，不知为何会把文章目录生成两次，略作修改。</p>
<p>路径在<strong>node_modules/hexo-asset-image/index.js</strong>，大约在<strong>48</strong>行左右。</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> same = link.split(<span class="string">''</span>).reduce(<span class="function">(<span class="params">acc, o</span>) =&gt;</span> !src.startsWith(acc += o) ? acc = <span class="string">''</span> : acc, <span class="string">''</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> res = link.slice(<span class="number">0</span>, -same.length).concat(src)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$(<span class="keyword">this</span>).attr(<span class="string">'src'</span>, config.root + res);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">console</span>.info &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">console</span>.info(<span class="string">"update link as:--&gt;"</span> + config.root + res);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="老婆"><a href="#老婆" class="headerlink" title="老婆"></a>老婆</h4><p>我采用的是部署在自己<strong>Github</strong>上的方式。</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/stevenjoezhang/live2d-widget.git themes/Next/source/live2d-widget</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>themes/Next/layout/_partials/footer.swig</strong>，<strong>14</strong>行。</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"copyright"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.min.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"/live2d-widget/autoload.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>themes/Next/source/live2d-widget/autoload.js</strong>，启用自己的路径。</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 注意：live2d_path 参数应使用绝对路径</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// const live2d_path = "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/stevenjoezhang/live2d-widget@latest/";</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> live2d_path = <span class="string">"/live2d-widget/"</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>路径在<strong>public/live2d-widget/waifu-tips.js</strong>，<strong>160</strong>行左右。</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (modelId === <span class="literal">null</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 首次访问加载 指定模型 的 指定材质</span></span><br><span class="line">  modelId = <span class="number">1</span>; <span class="comment">// 模型 ID</span></span><br><span class="line">  modelTexturesId = <span class="number">50</span>; <span class="comment">// 材质 ID</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>themes/Next/source/live2d-widget/waifu.css</strong>，<strong>24</strong>行，注释<strong>left</strong>，添加<strong>right</strong>。</p>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-id">#waifu</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">bottom</span>: -<span class="number">1000px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">/* left: 0; */</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">right</span>: <span class="number">100px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">line-height</span>: <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">position</span>: fixed;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">transform</span>: <span class="built_in">translateY</span>(<span class="number">3px</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">transition</span>: transform .<span class="number">3s</span> ease-in-out, bottom <span class="number">3s</span> ease-in-out;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">z-index</span>: <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="搜索"><a href="#搜索" class="headerlink" title="搜索"></a>搜索</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-generator-searchdb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>然后<strong>759</strong>行左右。</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">local_search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在博客的<strong>_config.yml</strong>中。</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 搜索</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">path:</span> <span class="string">search.xml</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">field:</span> <span class="string">post</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">content:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">format:</span> <span class="string">html</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="Refer"><a href="#Refer" class="headerlink" title="Refer"></a>Refer</h3><p><a href="https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000005723321" target="_blank" rel="noopener">阿里云<strong>VPS</strong>搭建自己的的<strong>Hexo</strong>博客</a></p>
<p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/Captain_Magicer/article/details/49073873?utm_source=blogxgwz8" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Hexo</strong>博客主题<strong>NexT</strong>使用自定义的<strong>CSS</strong>样式</a></p>
<p><strong><a href="https://github.com/EYHN/hexo-helper-live2d" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo-helper-live2d</a></strong></p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>配置</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>HEXO</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>关于内网穿透的一些配置</title>
    <url>/Configure-Intranet-Penetration/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>连一下老师安排的服务器<strong>Orz</strong>。</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h3 id="外网服务端"><a href="#外网服务端" class="headerlink" title="外网服务端"></a>外网服务端</h3><h4 id="Go环境的安装"><a href="#Go环境的安装" class="headerlink" title="Go环境的安装"></a>Go环境的安装</h4><p>下载包。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https:&#x2F;&#x2F;dl.google.com&#x2F;go&#x2F;go1.12.5.linux-amd64.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>解压。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo tar -C &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local -xzf  go1.12.5.linux-amd64.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>编辑环境变量。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim ~&#x2F;.bash_profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>添加变量。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">export PATH&#x3D;$PATH:&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;go&#x2F;bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>加载环境变量。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">source ~&#x2F;.bash_profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="NPS的安装"><a href="#NPS的安装" class="headerlink" title="NPS的安装"></a>NPS的安装</h4><p>下载。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;cnlh&#x2F;nps&#x2F;releases&#x2F;download&#x2F;v0.23.2&#x2F;linux_amd64_server.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>解压。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -zxvf linux_amd64_server.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>编辑配置文件。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim conf&#x2F;nps.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>修改密码和连接秘钥。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">public_vkey&#x3D;123</span><br><span class="line">web_username&#x3D;admin</span><br><span class="line">web_password&#x3D;123</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="创建客户端"><a href="#创建客户端" class="headerlink" title="创建客户端"></a>创建客户端</h4><p><strong>client</strong>→<strong>new</strong>，然后填个<strong>remark</strong>。</p>
<h4 id="创建Socks5"><a href="#创建Socks5" class="headerlink" title="创建Socks5"></a>创建Socks5</h4><p>填入要连接的内网<strong>IP:PORT</strong>，以及开放连接的外网<strong>PORT</strong>，再选择好上一步创建的客户端。</p>
<h3 id="内网客户端"><a href="#内网客户端" class="headerlink" title="内网客户端"></a>内网客户端</h3><h4 id="NPC的安装"><a href="#NPC的安装" class="headerlink" title="NPC的安装"></a>NPC的安装</h4><p>下载。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;cnlh&#x2F;nps&#x2F;releases&#x2F;download&#x2F;v0.23.2&#x2F;linux_amd64_client.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>运行。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.&#x2F;npc -server&#x3D;123.123.123.123:123 -vkey&#x3D;123 &gt;&#x2F;dev&#x2F;null 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这玩意不太稳定，所以起个定时任务。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#!&#x2F;bin&#x2F;bash</span><br><span class="line">count&#x3D;&#96;ps -ef |grep npc | wc -l&#96;</span><br><span class="line">if [ $count -le &#39;3&#39; ]; then</span><br><span class="line">echo $count</span><br><span class="line">cd &#x2F;root&#x2F;nps</span><br><span class="line">.&#x2F;npc -server&#x3D;123.123.123.123:123 -vkey&#x3D;123 &gt;&#x2F;dev&#x2F;null 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="本地客户端"><a href="#本地客户端" class="headerlink" title="本地客户端"></a>本地客户端</h3><p>装个<strong>Proxychains</strong>。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brew install proxychains-ng</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>编辑配置文件。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;etc&#x2F;proxychains.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>启用<strong>dynamic_chain</strong>，注释<strong>strict_chain</strong>，并在最后添加<strong>socks5</strong>。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">socks5 123.123.123.123 123</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>连接内网服务器。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">proxychains4 ssh root@172.123.123.123</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="Refer"><a href="#Refer" class="headerlink" title="Refer"></a>Refer</h3><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/RBPicsdn/article/details/90056270" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在<strong>CentOS</strong>上安装<strong>Go</strong>语言环境</a></p>
<p><a href="https://post.smzdm.com/p/a07md2nr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">超强内网穿透<strong>nps</strong>解决所有无公网IP问题</a></p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>配置</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>内网穿透</tag>
        <tag>服务器</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>KALI安装后的一些准备</title>
    <url>/Configure-Kali/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>心血来潮把笔记本以<strong>KALI</strong>作为了主系统。<br>安装完后为满足日常需求自然是需要做一些设置的。</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h3 id="更新源"><a href="#更新源" class="headerlink" title="更新源"></a>更新源</h3><p>终端输入如下命令打开。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">leafpad &#x2F;etc&#x2F;apt&#x2F;sources.list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>然后我这里使用清华大学的源。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deb http:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main contrib non-free</span><br><span class="line">deb-src https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&#x2F;kali kali-rolling main contrib non-free</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>然后如下命令是更新软件。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt-get update &amp;&amp; apt-get upgrade &amp;&amp; apt-get dist-upgrade</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="蓝牙"><a href="#蓝牙" class="headerlink" title="蓝牙"></a>蓝牙</h3><p>蓝牙启动。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">service bluetooth start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>蓝牙开机自启。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">update-rc.d bluetooth enable</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="QQ"><a href="#QQ" class="headerlink" title="QQ"></a>QQ</h3><p>然后安装<strong>wine</strong>来支持<strong>qq</strong>的启动，开启<strong>32</strong>位兼容。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dpkg --add-architecture i386</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装<strong>wine</strong>。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt-get install wine32</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>然后把清风师傅那边下载的<strong>wineqq</strong>解压放在<strong>home</strong>目录下，打开菜单就能启动。</p>
<h3 id="搜狗拼音"><a href="#搜狗拼音" class="headerlink" title="搜狗拼音"></a>搜狗拼音</h3><p>安装一下搜狗拼音。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt-get install fcitx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装从官网下载的搜狗拼音。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dpkg -i &#39;&#x2F;root&#x2F;下载&#x2F;sogoupinyin_2.2.0.0108_amd64.deb&#39;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>自动安装依赖包。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt --fix-broken install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="谷歌浏览器"><a href="#谷歌浏览器" class="headerlink" title="谷歌浏览器"></a>谷歌浏览器</h3><p>安装官网下载的谷歌浏览器。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dpkg -i &#39;&#x2F;root&#x2F;下载&#x2F;google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb&#39;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>由于我使用的是<strong>root</strong>用户，所以无法直接打开。</p>
<p>使用文件管理器打开路径<strong>/usr/share/applications/</strong>找到<strong>google-chrome</strong>的图标。</p>
<p>鼠标右键打开属性，在命令一栏<strong>/usr/bin/google-chrome-stable %U</strong>的后面加上<strong>- -no-sandbox</strong>。</p>
<p>给火狐浏览器安装中文包，先查看一下火狐浏览器的版本。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">firefox --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>52.7.3</strong>，然后去这个地址下载安装。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http:&#x2F;&#x2F;ftp.mozilla.org&#x2F;pub&#x2F;firefox&#x2F;releases&#x2F;52.7.3esr&#x2F;linux-x86_64&#x2F;xpi&#x2F;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装网易云音乐，值得一提的是官网上的<strong>debian</strong>版本装不了，需要下载<strong>ubuntu</strong>的安装。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dpkg -i &#39;&#x2F;root&#x2F;下载&#x2F;netease-cloud-music_1.1.0_amd64_ubuntu.deb&#39;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>然后同谷歌浏览器一样需要在<strong>sudo netease-cloud-music %U</strong>后加上<strong>–no-sandbox</strong>。</p>
<h3 id="十六进制编辑器"><a href="#十六进制编辑器" class="headerlink" title="十六进制编辑器"></a>十六进制编辑器</h3><p>安装</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt-get install ghex</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>然后<strong>Python</strong>和<strong>C</strong>的编译器我选择的是<strong>Pychram</strong>和<strong>Clion</strong>。</p>
<p><strong>Markdown</strong>选择的是<strong>Typora</strong>。</p>
<p><strong>Html+Css+Js</strong>使用的是<strong>Brackets</strong>。【这个也得像谷歌和网易云音乐一样加<strong>–no-sandbox</strong>。</p>
<p>就这样，<strong>desu</strong>。</p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>配置</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>Kali</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>关于MacBookPro的环境配置</title>
    <url>/Configure-MacBookPro/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>整理一下日常配置。</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h3 id="IDE"><a href="#IDE" class="headerlink" title="IDE"></a>IDE</h3><ul>
<li><strong><a href="http://www.jetbrains.com/pycharm/download/download-thanks.html?platform=mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PyCharm</a></strong></li>
<li><strong><a href="http://www.jetbrains.com/phpstorm/download/download-thanks.html?platform=mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PHPStorm</a></strong></li>
<li><strong><a href="http://www.jetbrains.com/idea/download/download-thanks.html?platform=mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener">IDEA</a></strong></li>
<li><strong><a href="http://www.jetbrains.com/ruby/download/download-thanks.html?platform=mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RubyMine</a></strong></li>
<li><strong><a href="http://www.jetbrains.com/go/download/download-thanks.html?platform=mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GoLand</a></strong></li>
<li><strong><a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/?dv=osx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VSCode</a></strong></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="云同步"><a href="#云同步" class="headerlink" title="云同步"></a>云同步</h3><ul>
<li><strong>OneDrive</strong></li>
<li><strong>iCloud</strong></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="文档编辑"><a href="#文档编辑" class="headerlink" title="文档编辑"></a>文档编辑</h3><ul>
<li><strong><a href="https://www.office.com/?auth=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Office</a></strong></li>
<li><strong><a href="http://typora.io/download/Typora.dmg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Typora</a></strong></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="插件"><a href="#插件" class="headerlink" title="插件"></a>插件</h3><ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/Southseast/WeChatPlugin-MacOS" target="_blank" rel="noopener">微信防撤回</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/Southseast/QQRedPackHelper" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>QQ</strong>防撤回</a></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="虚拟化"><a href="#虚拟化" class="headerlink" title="虚拟化"></a>虚拟化</h3><ul>
<li><strong><a href="https://download.docker.com/mac/stable/Docker.dmg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Docker</a></strong></li>
<li><strong><a href="https://www.vmware.com/go/getfusion" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VMware Fusion Pro</a></strong><ul>
<li>激活码 <strong>XKZYV-PK9CC-A1Y0X-K5HZL-Y65ZV</strong></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="数据库管理"><a href="#数据库管理" class="headerlink" title="数据库管理"></a>数据库管理</h3><ul>
<li><strong><a href="https://xclient.info/s/navicat-premium.html#versions" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Navicat Premium</a></strong></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="运维"><a href="#运维" class="headerlink" title="运维"></a>运维</h3><ul>
<li>SSH<ul>
<li><strong><a href="https://github.com/fitztrev/shuttle/releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Shuttle</a></strong></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>SFTP<ul>
<li><strong><a href="https://xclient.info/s/transmit.html#versions" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Transmit</a></strong></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>桌面远程<ul>
<li><strong><a href="https://install.appcenter.ms/orgs/rdmacios-k2vy/apps/Microsoft-Remote-Desktop-for-Mac/distribution_groups/All-users-of-Microsoft-Remote-Desktop-for-Mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Remote Desktop</a></strong></li>
</ul>
