ES['USERNAME']&#125;"</span> = <span class="string">'admin'</span> ]] &amp;&amp; [[ $&#123;username&#125; = <span class="string">'admin'</span> ]]</span><br><span class="line">$   then</span><br><span class="line">$       get_flag1</span><br><span class="line">$   fi</span><br><span class="line">$ fi</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/html&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>可以看到这边的逻辑是登陆为<strong>admin</strong>就可以拿到<strong>flag</strong>，同时利用路径穿越查看其他泄漏出的路径。然后在<strong>/post.wtf?post=../users/</strong>中发现<strong>admin</strong>用户的<strong>token</strong>，就可以伪造登陆来获得<strong>flag</strong>。</p>
