<h3 id="WEB11"><a href="#WEB11" class="headerlink" title="WEB11"></a><a href="http://123.206.31.85:3030/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WEB11</a></h3><p>依提示访问<strong>robots.txt</strong>，再指向<strong>shell.php</strong>，再根据题目写脚本。</p>
